title: WHIRLING F1 / GARTE barks
description: Garte says the phone is disconnected.

dialogueTree.title: Garte, the Cafeteria Manager: ""Yeah, it will be another week befo..."
dialogueTree.english: "Yeah, it will be another week before the phone company gets around to sending a repair guy."
dialogueTree.polish: „Tak, firma telefoniczna przyśle kogoś, kto to naprawi, dopiero za tydzień”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Так, тэлефонная кампанія дашле кагосьці, хто гэта адрамантуе, толькі праз тыдзень".
